    "longBusinessSummary": "Abdullah Saad Mohammed Abo Moati for Bookstores Company engages in the retail and wholesale trading of stationery, computers, and other accessories in the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia. The company is involved in the wholesale trading of office supplies, leather products and travel accessories made of leather or leather substitutes, bags, home furniture and furniture, office stationery, wooden, cork and plastic products, children's toys, computers and their accessories, and office furniture. It also engages in the retail of computers and their accessories, stationery and office tools, newspapers, magazines, libraries, and art supplies for drawing, as well as accessories and clothing accessories, such as gloves, ties, suspenders, prayer beads, and umbrellas. In addition, the company is involved retail sale of stationery, office supplies, newspapers, and magazines through bookstores. Further, it engages in the sale of printers and inks, as well as the leasing of buildings for commercial and residential purposes. Abdullah Saad Mohammed Abo Moati for Bookstores Company was founded in 1994 and is headquartered in Riyadh, the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia.",
